{"tid":1169321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟傳停接華為新訂單","createTime":"2019-05-24T09:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:33:37.000Z","uid":54733,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2462ee93158892137a27e7f32f672f0b6270b443","tid":1169321,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】隨着美國封殺華為，全球多間企業相繼宣布暫停與華為的業務往來。《南華早報》引述消息人士報道，美國科技巨頭微軟(Microsoft)已停接華為的新訂單。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，華為筆記型電腦上的Windows作業系統和其他內容相關的服務均受影響。至於現有華為個人電腦(PC)的Windows作業系統不會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，微軟的服務團隊亦已遷離華為深圳總部。<br />\n<br />\n外電稍早前報道，微軟將華為從旗下提供雲設備的網站Azure Stack之產品目錄上刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/509488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F509488&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=8e4a5e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/509488</a>"},{"pid":"e7460bf12c849589e9ce1d99fdc004692470d873","tid":1169321,"uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"支那要硬起來了"},{"pid":"bd1ce0162bf0748240d622e37e889d180a0408da","tid":1169321,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"自煮燃發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84df77ea8e62f39a85c912aac2c984e55da43ba2","tid":1169321,"uid":62532,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"你成功啦Mr A， 你個宗教會多13億信徒"},{"pid":"e6979340a8e26dc5426a20de76fb6e5cf98b8022","tid":1169321,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"真唔真，微軟咁有腰骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026876edee510f2833d4e8f9927a08c789ae61bd","tid":1169321,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re